Addon description, author, date, version
========================================
Artem Levagin
07.05.2016

This addon helps to speed up search by attributes when DB has 10K and more products.
It builds temp flat table for product attributes and optimize search query by reducing joint tables


History
========================================



Documentation
========================================
Required MYSQL right to CREATE and DROP tables

Set attributes fields in your include/config.local.ini file as:
  
[flat_attributes_search]
fields=field_name_1,field_name_2,field_name_3,field_name_4


